{"tid":2463390,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"點解橄欖鎮IGN比7分搞到日本炎上，但一個世界IGN比5分但風平浪靜","createTime":"2021-03-26T15:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T17:21:21.000Z","uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06456de3d870a0cbe0864c4e19e86598fcf3fe01","tid":2463390,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbdF1xXhCX62ytpM6BUSB4xZ88tmXUGJJ6Eb7edHDPvhx?filename=0agtLhq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0agtLhq.png&h=41660ac3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n橄欖鎮<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb943kKA5QRrasi8TZsyDgr1Ux9KAFZYVWHCFM29CFfDX?filename=5UVuuKc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5UVuuKc.png&h=5d03677e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一個世界<br />\n<br />\n原因係：<br />\nA. 25周年驚世巨作點知係鳩hea之作，你叫班正版支持者點樣對住班老翻打飛機呀？<br />\nB. 扑你個街，豐收之月來架！都無人玩架啦！Natsume執柒左佢啦！<br />\nC. 預左Natsume交行貨的手機遊戲，無期望自然唔會失望。<br />\nD. 語言障礙：日本仔唔識睇英文，想炎上都做唔到。<br />\nE. 玩家比星露谷寵壞左，今次仲要抄翻星露谷轉頭(仲要抄得差)，激嬲埋星露谷粉絲。<br />\nF. 仲有無其他？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUELpBoqj2WBaySXDiGs59MtMFWmMR8uD7uBesfc6NDhw?filename=ywvyb0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fywvyb0U.png&h=03602b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我今次決定以身試毒，睇下隻老翻牧場物語係咪傳聞中咁垃圾，Steam上面個極度好評係咪水軍來？<br />\n<br />\n仲有網上經常批評老翻牧場物語畫面粗製濫造好似手機遊戲，呢點我係絕對唔同意！<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQgWFoB3N2Q1prAxvaxtwXFE396vYxtPzFZACTrTkpedY?filename=uWdTb1H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWdTb1H.png&h=c7057092&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n因為本身老翻牧場物語就係手機遊戲！"},{"pid":"424be62bbb193e090cc748dda620b0992218e88d","tid":2463390,"uid":152768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"無人care呢啲非正統又唔出名既5分作品"}]}